<container label="Box" type="box">1
	</container>
	<container label="Folder" type="folder">2
	</container>	
</did>
		<scopecontent>
		<p>Contains a variety of council documents, including caveats issued against various individuals, orders of council, permission for a survey, and a memorial submitted by George Washington on behalf of a number of officers and soldiers for shares in 200,000 acres of land promised by Lt. Gov. Dinwiddie. Items are dated 1743, 1745, 1748, 1758, 1764, and 1772-1774.  
		</p>
		</scopecontent>
	<arrangement>
		<p>Arranged chronologically.
		</p>
		</arrangement>
	</c02>
