	<container label="Folder" type="folder">4
	</container></did>
		<scopecontent>
		<p>Contains copies of court orders, including statements claiming land under the royal charter from Great Britain and deeds of assignment. Items are dated 1750, 1763, 1770, 1775, and 1779.  
